data.description: Spacious home in great location of California City. Close to schools, shopping, churches, post office and bus lines The Living room is open to formal dining area with wood burning fireplace. Kitchen has white cabinets and butcher wood countertops. There is a breakfast nook with a sliding glass door to backyard. Features a covered patio with wood fencing. There is a (2) car garage and washer/dryer hook up is inside the home at hall. Upgraded fixtures and lighting. Property has regular sewer, no septic. Call for you private showing today!
